snippet.title: MannaRites (Early Access) - Magic Update Trailer
snippet.description:
First big content update is coming to MannaRites very soon!
Featuring new playable character - Magus!
And tons of other stuff as well =)

Game is available for free right here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1369770/MannaRites/

Welcome for our Discord server for latest news and to leave feedback
https://discord.gg/TrFJrCr
